msgid "CITY_REGION_301_DESC"
msgstr ""
"A thriving great city with a dense population and bustling merchants, an "
"important place for trading heavenly materials and earthly treasures and for "
"seeking opportunities."

msgid "CITY_REGION_301_NAME"
msgstr "Qingyun City"

msgid "CITY_REGION_302_DESC"
msgstr ""
"A small trade city in a desert oasis, where caravans pass through without "
"end and cultivators gather for supplies and exchange."

msgid "CITY_REGION_302_NAME"
msgstr "Shazhou City"

msgid "CITY_REGION_303_DESC"
msgstr ""
"A cultivation town deep in the forest; though less bustling than the famous "
"capitals, it is still home to many cultivators and is ideal for cultivation "
"and artifact refining."

msgid "CITY_REGION_303_NAME"
msgstr "Cuilin City"

msgid "CITY_REGION_304_DESC"
msgstr ""
"A flourishing great city at the river mouth, where waterways prosper and "
"water-aspect cultivators gather in great numbers."

msgid "CITY_REGION_304_NAME"
msgstr "Canglan City"

msgid "CITY_REGION_305_DESC"
msgstr ""
"A small mountain city perched atop endless peaks, shrouded in mist year-"
"round and rich in pure spiritual qi, an excellent place for ascetics to "
"comprehend the Heavenly Dao."

msgid "CITY_REGION_305_NAME"
msgstr "Lanyue City"
